					</note>
					<note><label>Colophon further notes:</label> Strangely, this final colophon (f.219v) is dated earlier than an internal colophon (f.135r): 14 Rabīʿ II 1108 / 10 Nov 1696. That internal colophon date is also stated to be year 39 of ʿĀlamgīr (i.e. Aurangzeb) which is inconsistent when compared to the colophon of volume 1 (1107, year 40).</note>
